high_descs: Walk around the center table to the left and turn right to face the knife on the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn left and walk forward and turn around to the right to face the trash can.
Cut the potato in the trash can into slices.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a slice of potato in the trash can.
Turn left and walk to the right around the table and turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn left and step forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Go left and around the counter to the back of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go to the end of the counter and face the trash can.
Cut the potato in the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a slice of potato from the trash can.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave above the stove and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato to the left of the potato on the shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the side of the island without the sink.
Pick up the gray knife from the table.
Turn left and go to the black trash can on the floor at the end of the island.
Slice the potato on the right in the trash can.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Take out one slice of potato from the trash can.
Turn left and go around the island to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator on the right.
Place the potato slice in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of heated potato in the fridge.
